content.rendered:
Vinyl cut self-adhesive sticker in the shape of ‘Spike’, our little thorny devil logo. ‘Spike’ loves exploring so stick him on your 4WD and take him to all your favourite places. Weight: 2 grams each. Size: 100mm long, 85mm wide, 0.1mm thick. Colour: Orange with Black outline. White background shown here is for clarity only. Shipping: We CAN ship this product to Post Office Boxes. Please note: Credit Card transactions are processed manually during normal business hours (AEST), not automatically at the time of ordering. Australian orders: Shipping cost is automatically calculated when ordering. International orders: Shipping cost is manually calculated once your order is received. You will be advised by email the total cost of your order including shipping (International shipping is NOT free). USA orders: Your order will be forwarded to our USA Distributor who will contact you to confirm your payment details and quote shipping costs (USA shipping is NOT free).
